### Hadith 1:486

*Narrated 'Aisha:*

Do you make us (women) equal to dogs and donkeys? While I used to lie in
my bed, the Prophet would come and pray facing the middle of the bed. I
used to consider it not good to stand in front of him in his prayers. So
I used to slip away slowly and quietly from the foot of the bed till I
got out of my guilt.

